    <p>What's that Feature?</p>
<p>When your code executes a <a href="https://api.drupal.org/api/drupal/includes!bootstrap.inc/function/variable_get/7">variable_get</a> what actually happens is that Drupal inspects the $conf global array variable to see if it contains an index with the variable name. It does NOT actually query the variable table.</p>
